00452     void setSrtpKey(const char* szKey, const int length)
00453     {
00454         int safeLen = (length < (int) sizeof(szSrtpKey)) ? length : (int) sizeof(szSrtpKey);

00465         memcpy(szSmimeKeyDer, szKey, safeLen);
00466         nSmimeKeyLength = safeLen;
00467     }

00484     const int getSrtpKeyLength() const  { return nSrtpKeyLength; }
